data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER IS NOW OFFERING A HUGE PRICE ADJUSTMENT to allow you to put your own personal touches on this home!! Welcome to your dream one story retreat. This exquisite 4 bedroom, 2 bath + office home is situated in a serene & picturesque location in Cypress Trails. The heart of the home, the chef's kitchen, features new appliances, modern cabinets, shiplap accents, & elegant light fixtures. The addition of a built-in dry bar w/wine fridge adds a touch of sophistication. How about those gorgeous BRAND-NEW FLOORS? The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living spaces, making it the ideal place for entertaining. Enjoy STUNNING water to preserve views from the screened/ covered lanai. This meticulously updated home blends style, comfort, and functionality, creating an ideal space for modern living. Don't miss this opportunity to make this house your home!
